#: .uk.EQUIPMENT_COMMANDMISSILE_UNCOMMON_PICKUP
msgctxt ".uk.EQUIPMENT_COMMANDMISSILE_UNCOMMON_PICKUP"
msgid ""
"{0}\n"
"<sprite name=\"Quality\"> Fire additional missiles for every missile related "
"item you have."
msgstr ""
"{0}\n"
"<sprite name=\"Quality\"> Випускає додаткові ракети за кожен ваш предмет, "
