#: .uk.EQUIPMENT_COMMANDMISSILE_UNCOMMON_DESC
msgid ""
"Fire a swarm of <style=cIsDamage>12</style> missiles, plus an additional "
"<sprite name=\"Quality\"> <style=cIsDamage>2</style> missiles for every "
