#: .uk.EQUIPMENT_HEALANDREVIVECONSUMED_UNCOMMON_PICKUP
msgctxt ".uk.EQUIPMENT_HEALANDREVIVECONSUMED_UNCOMMON_PICKUP"
msgid ""
"{0}\n"
"<sprite name=\"Quality\"> Lures nearby enemies to attack the sprout, all "
"damage dealt to it is converted into healing."
msgstr ""
"{0}\n"
"<sprite name=\"Quality\"> Паросток провокує ворогів атакувати його. Уся "
"завдана йому шкода конвертується у зцілення."

#: .uk.EQUIPMENT_HEALANDREVIVECONSUMED_UNCOMMON_DESC
msgid ""
"{0}\n"
"<style=cIsUtility>Lures</style> nearby enemies to attack the sprout, "
