"damage dealt to it. Increases sprout duration by <sprite name=\"Quality\"> "
"<style=cIsUtility>1</style> second."
msgstr ""
"{0}\n"
"<style=cIsUtility>Провокує</style> ворогів поблизу атакувати паросток та "
