msgid ""
"{0}\n"
"At <style=cIsUtility>5 or more charges</style>, using your "
"<style=cIsUtility>Primary skill</style> consumes <style=cIsUtility>5 "
"charges</style> and creates a <style=cIsDamage>lightning storm</style> in a "
"<sprite name=\"Quality\"> <style=cIsUtility>30m</style> range around the "
"target, dealing <sprite name=\"Quality\"> <style=cIsDamage>2000%</style> "
"<style=cStack>(+1600% per stack)</style> TOTAL damage."
