"<style=cIsDamage>5m-100m</style> radius <style=cIsDamage>kinetic explosion</"
"style> on hitting the ground, dealing <sprite name=\"Quality\"> "
"<style=cIsDamage>1300%-13000%</style> <style=cStack>(+300%-3000% per stack)</"
